01:25:56.882 --> 01:25:58.057
It's pretty bad in here.

1501
01:25:59.841 --> 01:26:02.191
I filed the papers
for the appeal.


1502
01:26:02.235 --> 01:26:05.281
And as I mentioned,
these things take time. Years.


1503
01:26:05.325 --> 01:26:08.676
-What do you suggest I do?
-Request protective custody.


1504
01:26:10.156 --> 01:26:11.287
What about the film?

1505
01:26:11.331 --> 01:26:13.159
Erica sold it to some network.

1506
01:26:14.116 --> 01:26:17.032
-Which one?
-Does it matter?


1507
01:26:17.076 --> 01:26:18.381
Yes, absolutely.

1508
01:26:19.992 --> 01:26:21.428
That's all I've got left.

1509
01:26:26.824 --> 01:26:27.825
We did it!

1510
01:26:29.262 --> 01:26:30.524
Hurry up, Caitlin!

1511
01:26:31.177 --> 01:26:33.788
Just give me a second.
I'm just gonna change.


1512
01:27:33.456 --> 01:27:35.981
"See, what a scourge
is laid upon your hate,


1513
01:27:36.764 --> 01:27:39.897
that Heaven finds means
to kill your joys with love.


1514
01:27:40.550 --> 01:27:43.031
And I, for winking
at your discords, too,


1515
01:27:43.075 --> 01:27:45.164
have lost a brace of kinsmen.

1516
01:27:46.078 --> 01:27:47.775
All are punish'd.

1517
01:27:49.342 --> 01:27:52.214
A glooming peace this morning
with it brings.


1518
01:27:52.693 --> 01:27:55.043
The sun for sorrow
will not show his head.

1519
01:27:55.696 --> 01:27:58.525
Go, hence, to have more talk
of these sad things.


1520
01:27:59.265 --> 01:28:02.007
Some shall be pardon'd,
and some punish'd.


1521
01:28:02.572 --> 01:28:05.445
For never was a story
of more woe


1522
01:28:06.098 --> 01:28:10.102
than this of Juliet
and her Romeo."